reviewText: An interesting title with great cover art. Is worth picking up. Was the movie good? Well, maybe. It was a tough watch at times.  Only pick it up if you want an obscure bad film in your collection.
Vampires are here in the south?  Very creative and humorous. Made me laugh. Nice twist on the on going vampire craze.

The sound was a little off but so are most of the true grinde house films I have watched over the years.
It was something diffrent and it pays off.
